Introduction

The global tax ecosystem is constantly evolving, and managing taxes is becoming more challenging for the tax & finance teams across the globe. Cygnet TaxTech offers technology enabled data-driven solutions to help large enterprises, small & medium scale businesses, and accounting practitioners with their indirect tax compliance requirements. With timely compliance, Cygnet TaxTech solutions enable taxpayers to avoid risks & penalties, be audit-ready, save time & costs, and enhance efficiency with end-to-end automation. We empower businesses to grow, enhance revenue, increase profitability and navigate digital transformation with our seamless, adaptive and consultative approach.

Trusted by brands across the globe

Discover Cygnet TaxTech architect

Cygnet TaxTech architect manages tax compliance of businesses with the building block structure & optimizes business processes by unlocking digital transformation through advanced data cleansing and custom system integrations & build operational efficiency.

Connect with Cygnet TaxTech architect

How can the Cygnet TaxTech architect help?

  • Evaluates tax and business processes and various data sources
  • Recommends accurate integration workflows
  • Automates data extraction for single source of truth
  • Offers the right platform with comprehensive features
  • Shares insightful reporting for apt decision making
  • Automate tax filing, reporting, & audits

Here is how we do it with our Building Block Structure!

Cygnet TaxTech architecture consists of a building block structure that can be customized as per the business needs transforming businesses digitally with custom-built automated solutions, system integrations, advanced data extraction & conversion engines and more to keep businesses compliant.

Tech-powered tax operations support businesses’ tax teams by analyzing data extracted from the source systems or ERP Systems. It helps them generate a single source of truth. Furthermore, the architect introduces high-performance servers with improved uptime to collate financial data via data warehouse, data lake, or application databases. The Cygnet TaxTech architecture will support businesses in Tax Return Scores, Invoice Verification, and Automation for efficient business processes. Here is your chance to create your architecture by selecting the best-suited system, processes, and requirements, the way you choose toppings for your pizza!
